channel.title: Neds Corner - Birds
channel.description: Area incorporating (ie. birds seen from) the Neds Corner property (Trust for Nature) and the adjoining Murray River frontage.

item.title: Certhionyx variegatus
item.dc:creator: chrisl
item.description: A small flock (<10) feeding over the revegetation area near the Sturt Highway.

item.title: Barnardius zonarius barnardi
item.dc:creator: chrisl
item.description: Feeding under exotic trees near the homestead.

item.title: Acanthiza nana
item.dc:creator: chrisl
item.description: Secretive and difficult to photograph on this occasion.

item.title: Pomatostomus ruficeps
item.dc:creator: colleenb
item.description: Captured on motion-sensor camera at bird bath.

item.title: Hirundo neoxena
item.dc:creator: chrisl
item.description: On the roof of the shearers' quarters at Neds Corner. Nesting also in the same building.

item.title: Cacatua galerita
item.dc:creator: chrisl
item.description: Curiously, not commonly encountered at Neds Corner.

item.title: Hydroprogne caspia
item.dc:creator: chrisl
item.description: Hunting along the Potterwalkagee Creek and Murray River.

item.title: Epthianura albifrons
item.dc:creator: russell
item.description: Ordinary photo (very long distance away) but confirms the species.

item.title: Plectorhyncha lanceolata
item.dc:creator: chrisl
item.description: Feeding on grubs hidden behind the seeds in the large pods of the Brachychiton tree in front of the Neds Corner homestead.

item.title: Ardea pacifica
item.dc:creator: russell
item.description: Ordinary pic but useful as confirmation of the record, a new record for the Neds Corner birds collection. Far away and flew off before I could get close.

item.title: Egretta novaehollandiae
item.dc:creator: russell
item.description: Ordinary pic but useful as confirmation of the record, a new record for the Neds Corner birds collection. Far away and flew off before I could get close.

item.title: Phalacrocorax carbo
item.dc:creator: chrisl
item.description: Photographed from the Neds Corner homestead.
